Art Naturals Konjac Facial Sponge
Description: Art Naturals is proud to present our konjac facial sponge set. Made from the roots of the konjac plant these purely organic sponges are incredibly gentle on your skin and face yet powerfully effective at exfoliating and cleaning clogged pores and flakey skin. Ideal for those suffering from acne, rosacea, dry flakey skin, or psoriasis. The organic makeup of our konjac sponge make them naturally ph balanced so free of impurities, sulfates, or parabens that they are literally edible. Suitable for even the most sensitive skin yet effective enough to see instant results. Konjac sponges are so much more than a simple cleaning tool. So natural and gentle konjac fibers clear pores and wash away dry and dead skin cells on even the most sensitive skin without irritation. The effects of rosacea, acne, blackheads, and dry flakes that are so difficult to buff away without irritating skin are cleansed and purified with ease. Because of its bouncy, rubbery texture konjac sponges create a rich lather while using less cleanser than you'd normally need with a washcloth or loofah. The natural fibers in our konjac sponges are so effective that they can be used to remove makeup and mascara with nothing but warm water.
